EXPLANATION
BY THE LEGISLATIVE COUNCIL
OF
A N A C T
RELATING TO CRIMINAL OFFENSES -- WEAPONS
***
1 This act would preclude an individual who has pled nolo contendere or been convicted of
2 a misdemeanor offense, and sentenced in accordance with the hate crime sentencing enhancement
3 act for such misdemeanor, from purchasing, owning, carrying, transporting or having in his or her
4 possession any firearm.
5 This act would take effect upon passage.
